text: Glad to see my so cal favorite is here when i come to town. Best Chili Burgers anywhere. A must go! Try the Tamales too. Yum!

boy we are so happy to finally have a little taste of southern california in our backyard. yeah we have fatburger & in & out too but bob's big boy folded up last year and that was our favorite. tommy's serves chili on everything so if you like chili head to tommy's. the burgers are huge & they load on the chili, the shakes are awesome, the fries are nice & crispy and loaded with chili & cheese. i wish they gave you an alka-seltzer with your meal though because you are gonna need it. the place looks great-alot like in & out, the service is very fast & friendly and the food is pretty darn good for a fast food joint. we posted this place last week as soon as we found it has opened and after a long day at the car show we had to make a pit stop for a long awaited bite of socal history!!

I've never heard of Tommy's until a late saturday night drive to Arby's. My little cousin about 13 was willing to try it with me! We got cheeseburger combo's with chili-fries!

I inhaled my cheeseburger and half my fries when my supposedly little cousin inhaled his burgers and both of our chili-fries. burger is ok but the hotdogs are really good. I'm craving it right now.

They are open pretty late for a late night snack. I always go to the one on st rose parkway!
